subject: Re: [junit] Why CVS on sourceforge of JUnit 4 reject anonymous visitor?
msgSnippet: Isaac, Unfortunately, SourceForge CVS has been intermittently unresponsive recently.  Usually if I wait two or three hours and try again, it allows me access.
messageBody:
Isaac,

me access. Good luck,
